ations\">\n  <div class=\"ir-hero-inner\">\n    <p class=\"ir-kicker\">Investor Relations</p>\n    <h1>Pool Safe Inc.</h1>\n    <p>TSX Venture Exchange: POOL — Corporate profile, filings, governance, and investor resources.</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-content-wrap is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-panel is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n\n<div class=\"ir-nav\">\n  <a href=\"/staging/investors/\" aria-current=\"page\">Investor Relations</a>\n  <a href=\"/staging/board/\">Board</a>\n  <a href=\"/staging/financials/\">Financials</a>\n  <a href=\"/staging/press/\">Press</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-actions is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"/staging/financials/\">Latest Financials</a></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"/staging/press/\">Latest Press</a></div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corporate Information</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns ir-grid-2 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corporate Address</h3>\n\n\n<p>906 Magnetic Drive<br>North York, ON<br>M3J 2C4<br>Canada</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stock Information</h3>\n\n\n<p><strong>Exchange:</strong> TSX Venture<br><strong>Symbol:</strong> POOL<br><strong>Sector:</strong> Consumer Discretionary</p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Auditors</h3>\n\n\n<p>Horizon Assurance LLP.</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corporate Counsel</h3>\n\n\n<p>Garfinkle Biderman LLP</p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transfer Agent</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<p><strong>TSX TRUST COMPANY</strong><br>200 University Ave., Suite 300<br>Toronto, ON<br>M5H 4H1<br><br><a href=\"https://www.tsxtrust.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">www.tsxtrust.com</a></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Governance &#038; Compliance</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"ir-doc-list wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/2025-Report-on-Fighting-Against-Forced-Labour-Pool-Safe-Inc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fighting Against Forced Labour &amp; Child Labour Report (2025)</a></li>\n<li><strong>Disclosure and Confidentiality Policy</strong> — <em style=\"color:#999;\">(Contact IR for access)</em></li>\n<li><strong>Compliance Report</strong> — <em style=\"color:#999;\">(Available upon request)</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Investor Relations Contact</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group ir-subsection is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n\n<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@poolsafeinc.com\">info@poolsafeinc.com</a><br><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href=\"tel:+14166302444\">+1 (416) 630-2444</a></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg-legal-counsel has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-c3cfcf2e wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-radius:8px;border-left-color:#0052ab;border-left-width:4px;background-color:#f2f7fb;margin-top:40px;padding-top:30px;padding-right:30px;padding-bottom:30px;padding-left:30px\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#023e8a;font-size:clamp(15.747px, 0.984rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.86), 24px);font-style:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase\">Legal Counsel</h2>\n\n\n<p><strong>Corporate Counsel:</strong> Miller Thomson LLP, 40 King Street West, Suite 5800, Toronto, Ontario M5H 3S1</p>\n<p><strong>Securities Counsel:</strong> Fasken Martineau DuMoulin LLP, 1200-600 Bay Street, Toronto, Ontario M5H 2R7</p>\n<p><strong>IP &amp; Technology Counsel:</strong> Gowling WLG, 1600-160 Elgin Street, Ottawa, Ontario K1P 1C3</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p><em>View Pool Safe&#8217;s public filings on <a href=\"https://www.sedar.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">SEDAR</a>.</em></p>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg-site-links-investors has-base-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-05d82636 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-radius:16px;margin-top:44px;padding-top:28px;padding-right:28px;padding-bottom:28px;padding-left:28px\">\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Related Investor Pages</h2>\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/board/\">Board of Directors</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/financials/\">Financials and Filings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/press/\">News and Press Releases</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/\">Home</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://loungenie.com/staging/financials/\">Financials</a></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-bloc